General.Name: Yojee Ltd
General.Description: Yojee Limited operates a cloud-based software as a service (SaaS) logistics platform that facilitates the flow of freight movements into a single ecosystem in the Asia-Pacific region. It offers various products, such as fleet tracking, route planning and optimization, delivery notifications, order and partner management, rating and cost calculations, reporting and insights, driver app, and electronic proof of delivery. The company also provides software subscription and related services, including SaaS software set-up services, software customization, and usage charges. It serves retail, manufacturing, and logistics industries. Yojee Limited is based in Subiaco, Australia.
